snippet.title: Some Girls | Series 1 | "I like sweet popcorn, you like salt"
snippet.description:
In this clip Amber tries but fails to dump Brandon after succumbing to the classic sad eyes technique.
Subscribe for more: http://bit.ly/hattricksub

Comedy about the lives and loves of a group of quirky 16 year old girls who play on the same school football team and live on the same inner city estate. We join them on their bumpy journey through adolescence taking in boys, sex, cliques, teachers, heartbreak, fun and even some football along the way. 

Talent: Adelayo Adedayo, Mandeep Dhillon, Alice Felgate, Natasha Jonas, Dolly Wells, Colin Salmon, Jassa Ahluwalia and Franz Drameh

For more information: 
http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00y78kd   http://www.bbc.co.uk/iplayer/episode/p01gkkbb/Some_Girls_Series_2_Episode_1/
